PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,FStormont has been urged to address the
OL,8,F"catastrophe" unfolding in Northern
OL,9,FIreland's hospital emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments (EDs).
OL,12,FA report by the Royal College of
OL,13,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM) stated that,
OL,14,Fin 2025, some 1,032 excess deaths were
OL,15,Fassociated with waits of 12 or more
OL,16,Fhours in EDs while awaiting admission.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,FThe body's State of Emergency Medicine
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland report found that,
OL,9,Fwhile the overall death figure for
OL,10,F2025 is slightly lower than in 2024
OL,11,F(1,122) and 2023 (1,063), the
OL,12,Festimated mortality figure has more
OL,13,Fthan doubled over five years.
OL,15,FIn 2020, the estimated mortality
OL,16,Ffigure was less than half of what it
OL,17,Fwas in 2025 ` at 461. A decade ago, in
OL,18,F2016, there were 60 excess deaths
OL,19,Fattributed to long waits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,FThe report also contends that
OL,8,Fovercrowding and long waits in EDs are
OL,9,Fnot the result of an increase in
OL,10,Fdemand, and that the numbers attending
OL,11,Fdepartments has "barely changed",
OL,12,Fwhile the number of long waits, and
OL,13,Fdeaths, have "skyrocketed".
OL,15,FIt found that in 2025, one in 12
OL,16,F(8.3%) patients waited 24 hours or
OL,17,Flonger, while a RCEM survey conducted
OL,18,Fin December 2025 found that one ED
OL,19,Frecorded a wait time of over 124 hours
OL,20,F` more than three days.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@`O]uD@NOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,FThe report makes a number of
OL,8,Frecommendations for the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Executive.
OL,11,FThese include ending corridor care and
OL,12,Fmortality associated with long waits
OL,13,Fin ED by the end of the decade,
OL,14,Fadopting a "whole-system approach to
OL,15,Fending ED overcrowding", with
OL,16,Fresponsibility for performance spread
OL,17,Facross the entire patient pathway.
OL,26,@vD@LOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,FThe recommendations also include
OL,8,Fensuring accountability for ending
OL,9,Fovercrowding and to implement measures
OL,10,Fto make excess deaths associated with
OL,11,Flong waits in ED to be treated with
OL,12,Fthe same seriousness as deaths in
OL,13,Fother medical specialties.
OL,15,FDr Michael Perry, Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fvice president for the Royal College
OL,17,Fof Emergency Medicine, urged that the
OL,18,Fsituation is treated like the
OL,19,F"catastrophe in need of redress that
OL,20,Fit is".
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"Behind these numbers are stories of
OL,8,Ffamilies ripped apart by avoidable
OL,9,Fdeaths which have happened because
OL,10,Fsuccessive governments have failed to
OL,11,Fgrab the ED crisis by the horns," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"We must not let the slight reduction
OL,15,Fon the previous year give us false
OL,16,Fassurance that the problem is being
OL,17,Ffixed. Such a glacial pace of progress
OL,18,Fis not good enough.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@aO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"Our health service has the highest
OL,8,Frates of long waits in EDs, and deaths
OL,9,Fper capita resulting from them, of any
OL,10,FUK nation. That statement should shock
OL,11,Four policymakers to the core.
OL,13,F"Politicians and system leaders need
OL,14,Fto treat this like the catastrophe in
OL,15,Fneed of redress that it is."
OL,17,FDr Perry said it is a "fixable
OL,18,Fproblem".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@\O]yD@WOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"While, sadly, we cannot help the
OL,8,Floved ones who have already
OL,9,Fexperienced a bereavement at the hands
OL,10,Fof a broken system, we know what
OL,11,Fmeasures can prevent future
OL,12,Fheartbreak," he said.
OL,14,F"Our report contains the answers.
OL,15,FAccountability, a whole-system
OL,16,Fapproach to patient flow and targets
OL,17,Fto ending corridor care and deaths
OL,18,Fassociated with long waits will make
OL,19,Fthe difference.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"We look forward to hearing from
OL,8,Fpolicymakers eager to put these
OL,9,Fmeasures in place."
OL,11,FA Department of Health spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "The minister and department
OL,13,Facknowledge the continued pressures on
OL,14,Four emergency departments.
OL,16,F"This is a complex problem with no
OL,17,Fquick fix but the only medium to long
OL,18,Fterm solution is to reduce demand and
OL,19,Fmanage demand differently.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]tD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"That means reducing the number of
OL,8,Fpeople coming through ED doors, as
OL,9,Fwell as getting people out of hospital
OL,10,Fas soon as they are fit for discharge
OL,11,Fto free up beds.
OL,13,F"Our reset plan is attempting, over
OL,14,Fthe next three years, to refocus our
OL,15,Fwork towards earlier support and
OL,16,Fintervention, prevention, providing
OL,17,Fneighbourhood-based care and
OL,18,Fencouraging people to take more
OL,19,Fresponsibility for their own health on
OL,20,Fa routine basis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"We are also looking at how we can
OL,8,Fcare for our frail elderly patients
OL,9,Fbetter by providing more care closer
OL,10,Fto home and preventing avoidable
OL,11,Fadmissions to hospital.
OL,13,F"However, we recognise that this will
OL,14,Ftake time to have an impact and it is
OL,15,Fnot helped by the very challenging
OL,16,Ffinancial position.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"In the interim, we will continue to
OL,8,Fmanage the quality of care we are able
OL,9,Fto provide to the best effect ensuring
OL,10,Fthe needs of our patients and staff
OL,11,Fremain our priority.
OL,13,F"The minister has discussed patient
OL,14,Fflow and hospital discharge issues
OL,15,Fwith HSC chief executives, and all
OL,16,Fagreed the need to increase community
OL,17,Fcapacity was the most important single
OL,18,Fchange that is required.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776387788
OL,3,CStormont urged to address
OL,4,C'catastrophe' in hospital emergency
OL,5,Cdepartments
OL,7,F"This is consistent with the reset
OL,8,Fplan towards a neighbourhood model of
OL,9,Fdelivery."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
